<h3 id="In_collaboration_with_Michael_Hardt">In collaboration with Michael Hardt</h3>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Antonio_Negri&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: In collaboration with Michael Hardt"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
