<li>Michael Hardt and Antonio Negri, <i>Labor of Dionysus: A Critique of the State-Form</i>. Minneapolis: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.upress.umn.edu/Books/H/hardt_labor.html">University of Minnesota Press</a>, 1994. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
