<p>Transcendence, Spirituality, Practices, Immanence: A Conversation with Antonio Negri by Judith Revel,  <i>Rethinking Marxism</i>, <i>28</i>(3–4), 470–478, (2016). <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222"><a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1080%2F08935696.2016.1243627">10.1080/08935696.2016.1243627</a>
